Description:
Style, space and spectacular views in a vibrant lifestyle locale
Flaunting breathtaking views from Victoria Harbour to Port Phillip Bay, this magnificent one-bedroom plus study apartment offers a flexible layout with spectacular indoor-outdoor appeal. Surrounded by Docklands many restaurants, cafés and bars, while just a free tram-ride into the CBD, the home provides an infinitely vivacious lifestyle, with literally everything at its door.
Perched on the twenty-sixth floor and spread with sleek Oak floors, the homes open plan layout and wide balcony delivers a light and airy feel, providing plenty of space to relax and dine with friends against a picture-perfect sunset view. The fully appointed kitchen makes catering a breeze, offering quality Miele cooking appliances and a handy dish-drawer among its stylish timber-look cabinetry.
A home office adds essential space for home-based work, while offering the flexibility as a separate dining room, while the generous robed bedroom entices a restful nights sleep against the glittery water-views, complemented by a stylish, fully tiled bathroom. Finished with a Euro laundry and secure carparking on title, and cocooned in todays best comfort and security, the home delivers a unique city-lifestyle, enriched by residents facilities including pool, spa, gym, library, business lounge and podium-level garden retreat.
Vacant possession now and private inspection could be organized at your convenience or during Christmas and New Year time.
Contact Nancy Jia 0430 770 820 for more details

Description:
Voguish Living @ The Mariner
Perched and hovering high on the 8th floor, cosy corner unit, of the beautiful "The Mariner" development. This north facing - perfectly situated apartment is overlooking at the magnificent water front view and would make a fantastic investment property investment with plenty of opportunity. Stunning, contemporary, this exquisite 1-bedroom apartment is completed with 1- bathroom, flawless layout, natural light flowing throughout that exudes style.
Featuring open plan living/dining area, opening out to private balcony, reverse cycle air-conditioning and built in robes. The well thought out stylish kitchen includes European appliances, gas cooktop, dishwasher, sleek timber cabinetry with separate pantry.
With plenty of on street parking at nearby Barassi Park, bike storage, public transport, Harbour Town shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and Citylink. The location is just fantastic.
Please contact Ary Tjin on 0423 891 891 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
NIGHT LIGHT VIEWS, RESORT FACILITIES
Luxuriating in breathtaking views and resort style amenities, this cutting-edge apartment redefines lifestyle excellence with its easy-care layout, convenient placement and exclusive resident only pool, gym and library. Bordered by a bank of windows, the open plan living, dining and kitchen zone draws in the twinkling night lights and beautiful daylight, while embracing stone benches and quality appliances. Each of the two bedrooms benefits from the inclusion of built-in-robes, one with private balcony, served by a sleek bathroom with toilet and Euro laundry. Finishing touches include split system heating/air conditioning for year-round climate control plus use of the state-of-the-art rooftop pool, gym, decked entertaining zone, library, private business centre, meeting rooms and cinema. A haven for those dreaming of a vibrant lifestyle, embracing easy access to restaurants, cafes, transport, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Train Station and the CBD.

Description:
GREAT INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
If you are an astute investor, dont miss out on this incredible apartment in the Docklands returning over 6%. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Marvel Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
With high returns in a sensation locale, this 2 bed, 2 bath apartment has fantastic views of the CBD, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms. A Euro-laundry, private balcony, split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, and secure car space round out this well designed apartment.
Typical of modern apartment living, residents enjoy the use of the heated outdoor pool and gymnasium.
With world class shopping and sporting events on your doorstep, this low maintenance investment is close to public transport and only minutes from City Link. Don't miss this amazing opportunity.

Description:
Brand New Brilliant Owner-Occupier or Investor Opportunity
Situated in the magnificent Marina Tower which offers state-of-the art facilities and a lifestyle embracing the benefits of both inner-city and waterfront living. Combining resort-style amenities with uninterrupted views of Victoria Harbour and the City skyline for your total enjoyment. This spacious, cutting-edge apartment features a generous living room and one bedroom - both opening to the balcony. Plus a sleek stone and prestige S/S kitchen and meals area, a sparkling bathroom, Euro laundry and basement car space.
Marina Tower The Docklands finest complex
Enjoy an ultra-convenient waterfront lifestyle
Video intercom security
Cutting edge interior
Sleek prestige S/S & stone kitchen
R/C heating & cooling
Secure basement car space
Exceptional owner occupier investment potential
Amenities
The spectacular Marina Tower, arguably one of the finest developments in the Docklands precinct offering residents resort-style amenities including access to a lobby lounge, library, meeting rooms. A private business centre, cinema, private dining room and kitchen, billiard room, rooftop lap-pool, expansive deck and fully-equipped gym.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of NewQuay with the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the fresh food complex The Market with its many gourmet offerings, butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

When location is more than just an address, youre sure to be impressed This well designed two-bedroom apartment is situated in the heart of Docklands with a plethora of amenities at your doorstep. An open plan design boasting light filled rooms, stone benchtops in the kitchen, separate bathroom, master with ensuite, good size balcony and secure off-street carpark. The open floorplan is complimented with floorboards throughout, air-conditioning, gas cook top/electric oven, remote intercom and more. An impressive fully equipped gymnasium, lap pool, meeting rooms, dance studio/room, BBQ facilities and resident garden area are just what open this complex to a world of luxury living. 883 Collins is only metres to the waterfront of the Yarra River, Woolworths, restaurants, cafes, medical suites, public transport, Port Phillip Ferries, Marvel Stadium and more. A quick stroll has you at Southern Cross Train Station, CBD, Flinders Street and so much more.

Description:
Immaculate Modern Charm
Perfectly located in the heart of Docklands vibrant NewQuay precinct is this charming, 'as new' one bedroom apartment in the desirable Marina Tower complex.
Enjoy the open-plan living zone bathed in sunlight with striking views & split system heating & cooling, a fabulous undercover balcony and chefs kitchen finished with stone benchtops & stainless steel appliances. The well-proportioned bedroom is fitted with a full wall of built-in-robes and is framed by floor-to-ceiling glass which captures Melbournes iconic Melbourne Star Wheel and far beyond. This home is an amazing city pad for owner occupiers or a sound addition if you're looking to start or grow your investment property portfolio.
AMENITIES
Residents will have access to building facilities including a 25m indoor swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and lobby with private meeting rooms.
LOCATION
An easy stroll to The District Docklands which features a brand new Woolworths, Dan Murphys ,Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, and a new fresh food precinct opening soon known as The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, and Dan Murphys. Youre also close to Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading universities, trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

Description:
First Class Living on the 12th Floor
Immaculate two-bedroom, two-bathroom property nestled nicely on the 12th floor of the Aqui Promenade complex. With water views and stylish contemporary interiors, floor-to-ceiling windows allows for great natural light. A spacious open living and dining area is well-served by a sleek kitchen with Miele appliances and plenty of cupboard space.
Designed by award winning architects Woods Bagot, Aqui Promenade was created to be a unique home for its residents, connecting them to the waterfront which is the main source of inspiration for its design, to the park at its doorstep and to the surrounding Docklands environment.
Explore the luxurious residents amenities at your disposal. Entertain friends on the rooftop garden or lounge amongst the leafy foliage in the sunshine. Work or study in peace, organise a last-minute meeting or relax with a book in the lounge and library. Time your pace in the 25m indoor pool or stretch your muscles in the gym.
You couldnt wish for a more convenient address. Superbly set on the citys edge, walk or catch the free city tram to the CBD, Southern Cross station, Waterfront City shopping, and Southbank Promenades riverside restaurants.
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for inspection
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
CHIC DOCKLANDS ONE BEDDER
Whether an investor or first home buyer, don't miss your chance to buy this smart one bed apartment in the Watergate Complex - surrounded by water, parkland, cafes, bars, and restaurants, it encompasses the best of cosmopolitan Melbourne on the doorstep of the CBD.
Located on the 11th floor this one bed, one bath apartment, features an open plan living/kitchen zone. The chic kitchen comes with stone bench-tops and dishwasher, whilst the bedroom comes with mirrored built-in-robes. The bathroom has clean modern finishes, heaps of storage, and laundry. Rounding out this slick inner-city pad is split system heating/cooling, and secure swipe/video intercom entry,
Designed with a premium lifestyle in mind Watergate offers its residents a 25 metre pool, spa, sauna, and gym. With public transport on your doorstep, a resort style facilities throughout, don't miss this superb opportunity to live in sensational location.

Loan Pre-Approved or cash buyers wanted!

Modern and timeless interiors frame stunning water and city views. Intelligent and generous floorplans offer abundant natural light, optimising view lines across the Yarra River, CBD and Victoria Harbour. The residence features high quality fixtures and fittings along with contemporary and sophisticated finishes that maximise luxury.
1 Collins Wharf represents Melbourne's affluent evolution. Enjoy living on new heights in this spacious one bedroom/two bedrooms with a carpark and a large balcony. At 1 Collins Wharf, cosmopolitan city living is an indulgence that rewards you with the best of urban design and the convenience of Melbourne’s world-class attractions. Explore all that Melbourne has to offer, or simply relax in your luxury apartment and enjoy the brilliant views. Swim in the pool, relax in the exclusive residents’ lounge or sample the finest local produce and dine in style when you book your space in 1 Collins Wharf’s fully-equipped kitchen. Enjoy and comfortably live in the world’s most livable city. Residents will enjoy exclusive access to luxury Club 1 Collins Wharf amenities including a swimming pool, cinema, billiards room, gym, yoga studio, private dining room, residents lounge and barbeque landscaped deck. City lifestyle meets garden living in tranquil rooftop garden space, where residents can relax and enjoy views of the surrounding cityscape.

Description:
Breathtaking views and sophisticated Yarra Point living
Enjoying magnificent views which include the iconic Melbourne skyline, Yarra River, and Port Phillip Bay, this 2 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom, 2 car space corner apartment in the coveted Yarra Point building is your quiet piece of the Docklands not far from the hustle and bustle of the CBD.
Expansive lounge and dining zones surrounded by bright floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for amazing vistas in almost all directions
Main living also lets you to take in breathtaking sunrise and sunset views
Amazing balcony terrace has an enviable corner position giving you direct views of the city and stunning Yarra River
Master bedroom includes a 2nd balcony with CBD views along with a designer dual vanity ensuite and built-in robes
Versatile study has the potential to be a 3rd bedroom
Stone kitchen is incorporated into the central living zone and comes with stainless steel Miele appliances
2nd bedroom with BIR and bay views
Central bathroom, European laundry
Central living area also features motorised blinds
Built-in robe storage fitted out with custom-made drawers and shelving
Ducted heating and cooling
Pre-wired for built-in speakers
Secure intercom entry
2 secure basement car spaces
AMENITIES
Residents of the Yarra Point complex have access to RekDek which features a swimming pool, spa, steam room, sauna, and gym. You can also use the buildings own gym, residents lounge, and communal garden.
LOCATION
Surrounded by green parklands, youll love this amazing Yarras Edge location close to so much that Melbourne has to offer. Nearby South Wharf Promenade offers superb restaurants and bars, while local eateries including Pizze Societe, Mad Duck Café, and Hooks At The Yarra always hit the mark. Youre not far from DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Marvel Stadium, MCG, cycling paths and rowing sheds, sensational CBD shops and restaurants, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station, while youre also only a 5 minute drive to the beach!

143m²

Heritage Splendor
An opportunity to purchase a cosy bachelor pad in one of Melbourne's most opulent heritage buildings in the form of this fully refurbished and fully furnished North facing apartment suitable for an owner occupier or investor. Offering one bedroom mezzanine style living with ducted heating and cooling approx. 56sqm in size. The building itself is a Melbourne land mark and offers features such as pool, spa, sauna, and gymnasium, onsite caretaker, piano Bar, restaurant and cafe. Description:
RIVERFRONT LUXURY
Led by luxury and making the most of wonderful water and city views, this super-spacious 2 bedroom apartment on the podium level of the award-winning T5 building is underpinned by a far-reaching 77sqm (approx.). Head downstairs and the best of Yarra's Edge and Docklands is on show with a short walk to public transport (including the free tram zone), DFO shopping, and South Wharf's restaurant and bars.
Discover an immediately inviting, open-plan living and dining area, complemented by the flawless finishes of a granite-topped, high-end kitchen boasting an entertainers' island bench and a built in fridge / freezer. Designed and styled for easy outdoor living, enjoy an instantly relaxed, northeast-facing balcony showcasing awe-inspiring water views of the Marina with the stunning city skyline providing a dramatic backdrop, day and night. Conveniently connected to the balcony, the oversized bedrooms share in the spectacular panorama, serviced by a sparkling bathroom with a fully tiled, walk-in shower and a concealed laundry. There is also some flexibility in the floorplan with a rewarding opportunity to increase returns for investors or for the owner occupier to reside in.
Comprehensive features include secure parking, heating / cooling, video intercom entry, ample storage, low Body Corporate fees, and premium lifestyle facilities with exclusive access to an indoor heated lap pool, spa, sauna, steam room and a fully equipped gym.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

78m²

MUST NOT MISS OUT!!!
302/815 BOURKE STREET, DOCKLANDS

Description:
Elegant Single Bedroom with Rare Water Vistas
Perfectly placed in one of the Docklands most exclusive complexes, The Quays, this beautifully-appointed and relaxed single bedroom residence embodies modern apartment living that is sure to captivate local professionals, first home buyers and smart investors.
Cutting edge single bedroom opportunity
Sleek stainless steel & stone Kitchen
R/C air conditioning
Resort style amenities
Enjoy an ultra convenient Docklands lifestyle
Exceptional owner occupier and investment potential
European laundry
Intercom security
Secure basement parking
Some of the best Victoria Harbour views in Docklands
Amenities
The comprehensive resort style amenities available to the lucky residents of The Quays tower include access to a heated swimming pool, sauna and spa, fully-equipped gym & yoga room, tennis court, rooftop garden with built-in gas barbeques and dining area plus a residents lounge including library, a private dining room, cinema, boardroom facilities and 24 hour concierge.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of NewQuay with the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the fresh food complex The Market with its many gourmet offerings, butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

51m²

Description:
A Chic New Quay Waterfront Lifestyle
This freshly painted home is superbly located in the Harbour 1 Tower which captures all the very vitality of a New Quay lifestyle. Enjoy a generous square floor-plan which allows for relaxed living and features a full-width northern balcony capitalizing on winter sunshine - perfect for indoor/outdoor entertaining and enjoyment. Whilst floor-to-ceiling glass walls deliver loads of natural light to the interior. An ideal starter for owner occupiers or a brilliant investment for a property portfolio - it offers a vibrant New Quay and Docklands lifestyle with all its attractions and convenient inner-city lifestyle benefits.
Loaded with features and convenience
Generous living/dining area plus a wide balcony
Stylish granite & stainless steel kitchen
Two bedrooms with BIRs
Sleek bathroom with laundry
R/C air conditioner
Secure intercom entry
Secure basement car parking
Amenities
All residents have access to the sauna and gymnasium plus an exclusive library/lounge for relaxation, quiet reading or entertaining friends plus an audio visual room for residents use. Also secure intercom entry and basement car parking with easy access to dining and transport options including the free tram zone or Southern Cross station.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of NewQuay with the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the fresh food complex The Market with its many gourmet offerings, butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
